# DeskGPT SC01 â€” ESP32-S3 Touchscreen Desktop Assistant

DeskGPT is a standalone GPT-powered personal assistant running on the WT32-SC01 Plus / Panlee SC01 Plus (ESP32-S3-WROVER-N16R2).  
It features a 3.5" capacitive touchscreen, Wi-Fi connectivity, and a modular UI system built with LovyanGFX.

## âœ¨ Features (current)
- ESP32-S3-WROVER (16MB flash, 2MB PSRAM)
- 3.5" 480x320 IPS LCD (ST7796) + capacitive touch (FT6336)
- Modular project layout (UI / network / OpenAI / audio / storage)
- Clean Wi-Fi manager
- OpenAI Chat API client (chat completions)
- Boot UI + status bar + chat pane layout

## ðŸ”’ Secrets
Real Wi-Fi credentials + API keys go into:
src/config_local.hpp
This file is **ignored** via `.gitignore`.

A template file is provided:
src/config_local.example.hpp
